BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 259.92 750 Td (WHAT IS OCD?) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Obsessive-Compulsive Disorder \(OCD\) is a neurobiological condition) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (affecting approximately 1 in 40 adults. It is NOT about being neat) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (or organized. OCD involves:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (OBSESSIONS: Unwanted, intrusive thoughts, images, or urges that) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (cause significant distress. These feel 'sticky' - you cannot simply) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (dismiss them. They are EGO-DYSTONIC, meaning they go AGAINST your) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (values and desires.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (COMPULSIONS: Repetitive behaviors or mental acts performed to) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (reduce the anxiety caused by obsessions. They provide temporary) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (relief but STRENGTHEN the OCD cycle long-term.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (KEY FACTS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (- OCD is NOT your fault - it is a brain-based condition) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (- Having a thought does NOT mean you want it or will act on it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (- Thought = just a thought, NOT a fact or prediction) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (- ERP \(Exposure & Response Prevention\) is the gold-standard treatment) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (- Recovery is possible - most people improve significantly with ERP) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (THIS WORKBOOK WILL HELP YOU:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (1. Understand your specific OCD patterns) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (2. Build an ERP hierarchy \(fear ladder\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (3. Practice systematic exposures) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (4. Track your progress over 12 weeks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (5. Develop relapse prevention strategies) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (IMPORTANT: This workbook works best alongside a therapist trained) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (in ERP. If you do not have one, look for an OCD specialist at) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 251 Td (iocdf.org or nocd.com.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
