BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 259.92 750 Td (TYPES OF OCD) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (OCD can latch onto ANY theme. Common subtypes include:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (CONTAMINATION OCD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (  - Fear of germs, illness, bodily fluids, chemicals) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (  - Compulsions: excessive washing, avoiding 'contaminated' objects) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (HARM OCD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (  - Intrusive thoughts about hurting yourself or others) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (  - Compulsions: checking, avoiding sharp objects, reassurance seeking) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (  - NOTE: Having these thoughts does NOT mean you are dangerous) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (SYMMETRY / 'JUST RIGHT' OCD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (  - Need for things to feel 'even' or 'just right') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (  - Compulsions: arranging, counting, repeating until it feels right) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (RELIGIOUS / SCRUPULOSITY OCD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (  - Fear of sinning, blasphemy, or offending God) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (  - Compulsions: excessive prayer, confessing, seeking reassurance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (RELATIONSHIP OCD \(ROCD\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (  - Constant doubt about love/attraction to partner) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (  - Compulsions: comparing, testing feelings, seeking reassurance) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (OTHER COMMON THEMES:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (  - Pedophilia OCD \(fear of being attracted to children - you are NOT\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (  - Existential OCD \(obsessing about reality, consciousness\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td (  - Health anxiety \(fear of having a serious illness\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (  - Perfectionism OCD \(fear of making mistakes\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 251 Td (MY OCD THEME\(S\): ________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 235 Td (My main obsessions: _____________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 219 Td (My main compulsions: ____________________________________) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
