stream
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 174.96 750 Td (CHALLENGING INTRUSIVE THOUGHTS - Part 2) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (COMMON COGNITIVE DISTORTIONS IN OCD:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (1. THOUGHT-ACTION FUSION: Believing thinking = doing) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (   'If I think about hurting someone, I might do it.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (   REALITY: Thoughts are NOT actions. Period.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (2. OVERESTIMATION OF THREAT: Believing danger is very likely) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (   'If I touch that doorknob, I WILL get sick and die.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (   REALITY: Your brain overestimates probability.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (3. INTOLERANCE OF UNCERTAINTY: Needing 100% certainty) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (   'I need to KNOW for sure that I locked the door.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (   REALITY: 100% certainty is impossible about anything.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (4. OVERIMPORTANCE OF THOUGHTS: 'If I think it, it matters') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (   'Having this thought means I am a terrible person.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (   REALITY: Thoughts are mental noise, not identity.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (5. NEED TO CONTROL THOUGHTS: Believing you should stop them) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (   'Normal people do not have these thoughts.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (   REALITY: Everyone has bizarre/disturbing thoughts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td () Tj ET
