BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 215.28 750 Td (DEFUSION TECHNIQUES FOR OCD) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (DEFUSION = Creating distance between YOU and your thoughts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (You are NOT your thoughts. You are the one OBSERVING them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (TECHNIQUE 1: Label It) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (Say: 'I notice I am having the thought that...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (Or: 'There is my OCD again, telling me...') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (Practice: ___________________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (TECHNIQUE 2: Sing It) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (Sing your obsessive thought to 'Happy Birthday' or 'Jingle Bells') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (This removes the emotional charge without suppressing the thought.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (TECHNIQUE 3: Thank Your OCD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td ('Thank you, OCD, for trying to protect me. I do not need your) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (help right now. I can handle this uncertainty.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (TECHNIQUE 4: The Leaves on a Stream) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (Imagine placing each thought on a leaf floating down a stream.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (Watch it pass. Do not grab it. Do not push it away.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (TECHNIQUE 5: Agree with OCD \(Paradox\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td ('Maybe I DID leave the stove on. Maybe the house WILL burn down.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (Agreeing sarcastically takes away OCD's power.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (TECHNIQUE 6: The Bully Metaphor) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (OCD is like a bully. The more you react, the more it bothers you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td (Responding with 'Maybe, maybe not' starves the bully.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (My favorite defusion technique: ______________________________) Tj ET

endstream
